<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=65&amp;p=393#p393"><![CDATA[
1122233444... is 2.5x scaling, presumably in a 2.5x by 2.0x setup.<br /><br />To get a proper 2.4x setup, try 1122a3344b55, where a=(2+3) mixed and b=(4.5) mixed. Or just do pixel doubling to a surface in video memory and use DirectX to stretch-blit it to the screen.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=9">tepples</a> — Tue Nov 30, 2004 9:34 pm</p><hr />
